headline: Citi upgrades Linde on project wins and productivity gains
summary: Investing.com -- Citigroup raised its rating on industrial‑gas maker Linde plc to Buy from Neutral and lifted its price target to $535 from $500, saying strong execution on price and productivity plus a deep backlog of clean‑energy projects should keep margins climbing even if demand stays patchy.
